quote.p:
—reduce PDRY forces in the Sixth
                                Governorate (see map) and halt all artillery bombardment of
                                Dhufar;

—moderate PDRY’s radical policies
                                and reduce PDRY’s export of
                                revolution to conservative Arab states;

—strengthen President Ali against more ideologically committed
                                leftists in the PDRY Government;
                                and

—PDRY’s diplomatic isolation
                                prevents Aden from receiving needed economic aid from the
                                oil-producing Arab states;
